summary:
Knowledge of the entire lifecycle of an automation system: customer requirements study; offer preparation; design and equipment selection; writing functional specification and schematics; configuration, programming and tests; commissioning and customer acceptance tests; punch list follow-up and aftersales support.
Industries: power generation, solar, oil and gas, pharmaceutical, food and beverage, transportation.
